Some angry youths on Wednesday burnt down Sotitobire Miracle Church in Akure Ondo state The church was set on fire after the corpse of a year old boy declared missing in the church some week ago was exhumed. Founder of the church, Prophet Alfa Babatunde has also been arrested. He is reported to be currently in the custody of the Department of State Security(DSS) in Akure, Ondo State capital. Details shortlyâ€¦